OL,7,FBrianna, 16, was stabbed 28 times with
OL,8,Fa hunting knife in a "sustained and
OL,9,Fviolent" assault inflicted with
OL,10,F"considerable force" to her head,
OL,11,Fchest, back and neck - including one
